description: CNN Model buildingAfter doing a lot of combination network depth number of neurons layer chaining batch size learning rate number of epochs optimizer. Recall name recall Accuracy Loss Predict. ScalingBring all values back to the same scale. I m working on improving it to reach at least 90 at the beginning with my initial architecture I was at 69 on the validation set. Get the class with the highest predicted probability. Precision name precision tf. There comes a time when the model does not learn anything new and only memorizes the training set. We want to obtain values between 0 and 1. We have 10 categories in total see image above. CIFAR 10 Images classification using CNN image_2021 02 25_100512. I ended up getting about 85 on the validation set with the architecture below. These are the label indexes and the indexes of the max probabilities Plot Import Tensorflow 2. Each probability at index i corresponds to the probability for the image in question to belong to the class i. Done Let s take a look at shapes Display some images from the dataset Data type conversion Categorical target Converting target variables to binary class matrix. So here for example in position 3 we have a probability of 1. Images are 32 32 and in RGB. This means that the model is 100 sure that the image passed to make this prediction represents a cat index 3. png data image png base64
